bio:
Tracey West is a children's book author who has written for many different licensed series, including Pokémon, SpongeBob SquarePants, and more. Tracey West was born and brought up in New Jersey, United States.

She has not only written Pokémon, but also Teen Titans and Power Puff Girls. She has also written her own original series, Pixie Tricks. Tracey West started her books on the 2000s. She has written over 200 books for children. - wikipedia
name: Tracey West
